{"tid":1974455,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】德國逐步解封 仍建議民眾帶口罩 法國延長封城多 4 星期","createTime":"2020-04-16T00:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T00:46:30.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8047b5b24b750b9508049f124f1a47e7980cdc9d","tid":1974455,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T00:46:30.000Z","msg":"歐洲多個國家逐步放寬防疫指引，最新的是德國宣布重開學校和部分商店，但法國則要延長抗疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n德國總理默克爾宣布逐步放寬抗疫指引，包括部分商店下周會重開，學校亦會在 5 月 4 日起陸續復課，但社交距離指引起碼會持續至 5 月 3 日，並建議民眾在商店或公共交通工具內要帶口罩。一些大型群眾活動，包括宗教活動，在 8 月底前仍然禁止。酒吧、咖啡店、戲院和音樂廳繼續關閉⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%90%E6%AD%A5%E8%A7%A3%E5%B0%81-%E4%BB%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E5%B8%B6%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E5%B0%81%E5%9F%8E%E6%94%BF%E7%AD%96%E5%A4%9A-4-%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2581-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25AD%2596%25E5%25A4%259A-4-%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%259C%259F%2F&d=t1SY3LDExWMfWGGt1HQTgPbhcgmijv%2F0DJBpEVBRbRs%3D&h=4387273b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2580%2590%25E6%25AD%25A5%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2581-%25E4%25BB%258D%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%25A